te><blockquote>根本就係極唔平等<br />\n<br />\n男有生理反應=自願<br />\n女有生理反應唔等於自願<br />\n<br />\n兩個未成年發生性行為<br />\n淨係告個男<br />\n女果個無份咁<br />\n<br />\n亂倫又淨係告男<br />\n想點呀</blockquote><br />\n女方0責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n女方實都係自願架  如果唔係就係強姦案啦</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170502/s00001/1493704369185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170502%2Fs00001%2F1493704369185&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BNwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=bff4ccdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170502%2Fs00001%2F1493704369185&h=526271f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170502/s00001/1493704369185</a><br />\n令我諗起哩單（今次quote 明報有寫清楚法官睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n「法官相信男子一時不受控下才令下體勃起，故難以確定他有非禮意圖。法官亦同意上訴人指，事主的證供有不一致的地方，對於非禮時間長短有不同說法，而在接受盤問時，亦明顯迴避作答辯方大狀問題。法官認為定罪不穩妥，裁定上訴得直，撤銷定罪。」<br />\n<br />\n其實都有案例改返相信被告「不受控才令下體勃起」<br />\n（男性生理反應但屬於不自願）<br />\n加上事主供詞不一同迴避問題而撤銷控罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但掉返轉嚟睇，係有哩兩個因素之下，初審都竟然罪成，我諗唔多唔少都對男被告唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa59fb9cfde91fe0267d7ca7f1e84612b6e140de","tid":343974,"uid":12565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:24:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起有個外國節目講家暴<br />\n個男事主係節目講佢點比人老婆施暴法 <br />\n之後台下班觀眾係到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩個主持即係開聲幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話如果今次事主係女 你班友實屌鳩佢老公唔係人乜乜乜</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7PR5ryhnYtQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7PR5ryhnYtQ&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BNwHu